Lagos State Senior Model College Badore (nke bụbu Lagos State Model College Badores) bụ ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị nke steeti dị n'obodo Badore, Eti-Osa Obodo gọọmentị nke Lagos Steeti
Ọ dị n'ime otu ogige ahụ dị ka ụlọ akwụkwọ dị ala
E hiwere ya n'afọ 1988, ya na kọleji anọ ndị ọzọ n'okpuru nchịkwa ndị agha nke Captain Okhai Mike Akhigbe, Gọvanọ ndị agha nke steeti Lagos n'oge ahụ
Kọleji nke e guzobere ya na mmadụ anọ ndị ọzọ malitere na Government College, Ketu, Epe
Kọleji anọ ndị ọzọ bụ Igbonla, Kankon, Meiran na Igbokuta
Site n'oge 1988 na 1992, e nyere kọleji ntọala dị mkpa ma lekwasị anya na ọrụ ha dị ka ndị na-aga n'ihu na agụmakwụkwọ na mbọ agụmakwụkwọ

Ụmụ akwụkwọ nọ na nwanne nwanyị Model College Igbonla meriri laurels na mmemme site na Directorate of Food Roads and Rural Infrastructure (DFRRI), All Nigeria Confederation of Principals of Secondary Schools (ANCOPSS) na ọtụtụ asọmpi ndị ọzọ
Dịka ọmụmaatụ, otu nwa akwụkwọ si na Igbonla College meriri ANCOPSS National Essay Competition n'afọ 1992
Onye isi ntọala maka Igbonla, James Akinola Paseda, ji okpukpu abụọ dị ka onye isi nhazi maka kọleji ise na mbido na Febụwarị  afọ 1988
Onye isi ntọala maka Badore bụ Oriakụ Arinze ebe osote onye isi bụ B.O
